set_guild_data

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_guild_data -  This method sets the data associated with the guild for the player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_guild_data(mixed * dat)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^dat%^RESET%^ - the data to associate with the guild
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/guild-race.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the data associated with the guild for the player.
This is used for stuff like the orders for wizards and the type of
specialisation for theives.
.EP

